Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:07.87,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本片輕描淡寫地講述了南家三姐妹平凡的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:10.20,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要過度期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參觀利子家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  利子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可以去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出門嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…那計劃表…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很急嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那不是計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我完美的計劃表有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了玩你還寫了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不學習嗎  學習
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
