Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:00:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃變得一團亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習→玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要重寫計劃表…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如加進學習之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  之類的之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地定下學習計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  marker筆的話就不能重寫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.98,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,300)}隱藏不住的曬痕與少女心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個占卜相當准的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子你還真喜歡占卜什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過利子你是天秤座的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣超差而且要注意水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候太准了也難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會要去泳池  要注意水的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在泳池…溺…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占什麼蔔  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的天秤座在吼叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是騙人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是胡扯的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭氣睡覺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿幸運色藍色的衣服運氣會不會好一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運物是玩偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來水會流到千秋那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過玩偶從災難手裡保護了天秤座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  不愧是幸運物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看它仿佛就是吸取大地水分的大樹一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈別感歎了快點拿東西把水擦乾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個占卜  是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我遲到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子不能進入泳池！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖…雖然占卜上是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳裝是藍色的至少會好點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  禁止利子接近泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是為了什麼來這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也來泳池了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡  你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱約看到些藍色的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  幸運色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子  和藤岡一起的話可以進入泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡  利子由於某種理由今天可能會溺水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你說不定可以改變這個命運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡  要緊握住利子的手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天運氣超差？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜什麼的真不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希和淳子好像在一起打工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應聘的時候會有面試之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會做些什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介紹興趣  特長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展示自已的長處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂自我PR啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我PR嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅長這種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅長的想法可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來練習吧！練習！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來當面試官問問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來面試  確認你適不適合當面試官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼千秋適合當面試官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  夏奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你自我PR
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子自我PR啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點難懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難懂麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再具體點的更簡單易懂的美少女就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍微失禮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺變得簡單易懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單易懂  合格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就合格了啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就交由我來擔當面試官了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  維持美少女的模式進行面試嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這麼說話有點怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不受理來自對方提出的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請自我PR一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經常被人說很開朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田小姐比昨天換下的螢光燈還要明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋小姐  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎餅的袋子太堅固了打不開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剪刀就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起面試更不擅長應對美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡先生  今天來訪我家的動機是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  動機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學打電話邀請我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  邀請什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我簡直就像是沒有禮儀的女子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  她怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樣子好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不受理來自對方提出的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只給你一個提示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂自我PR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是把自己是怎麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在考慮些什麼傳達出去就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你自我PR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  現在的我滿腦子只想做這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡平常的南夏奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽到這句話的話  就一直要演下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:46.94,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}恐怖～～谷  篇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.95,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}恐怖～～沙漠  篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們一起去把太平洋遊個遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  下海之前要先做準備運動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來海邊要事先我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要做心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是穿著泳裝麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備地多充分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你說穿了過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  今天吉野在場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她面前穿泳裝太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野說不定注意到了我的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍不換上泳裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天似乎有點感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想讓阿珍來教我游泳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍微休息下就好了  你先游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會真希和淳子也會過來匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  千秋她們已經去游了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  要塗防曬油嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你塗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍滿臉通紅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香到底用了什麼絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要放手  不能放哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  相信我吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆身體  只動腿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋可不會游泳  溺水了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:14:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想讓你們知道大海的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈你是姐姐  做事之前也考慮下後果吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這海參當我道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為阿珍你說不放手的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也要一直做朋友喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  剛才謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你喜歡海參嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你  我和千秋變得要好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你邀請我一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能來海邊真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到最後都不要鬆懈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回去之前都是海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工很快就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和春香她們一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  炒麵就是要像皮筋一樣有嚼勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這微微的焦味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然咖喱有分歐洲和印度等各種風味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個是速食咖喱包的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵要泡得有些糊了再吃才算賺到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說都很難吃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個說出來就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易來一趟海邊  都被你給糟蹋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像都沒食欲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋好像很失落的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算只有一個人失落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也開心不起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋就交給我吧  你們就去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為有你這種人去照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才讓她誤以為這是理所應當的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春香把千秋寵壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  說得過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就一定要說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋之所以會變得失落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是因為夏奈說得太過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會去理會沒有協調性的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了那麼多次要等大家一起切西瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛都因為我  害得大家都沒怎麼吃東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想現在大家可能餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想負起責任把西瓜切好給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦  千秋  沒有人在生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  反正你就是個好好先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就來玩切西瓜吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊  右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…稍微往左一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這是…又甜又多汁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘著沙子的部分尤其好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  應該是難吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不去理會她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看這曬痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  完美地曬出了泳裝的痕跡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是之前和你們去海邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天之後  我的夏天就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但不能和修一他們去游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡也不能光著身子到處跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時不能在別人面前露出自己的身體了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了羞澀的少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有著恥辱曬痕的男子漢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那個創口貼是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊  是之前返校的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是去一次校醫室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  我會一輩子珍惜這個創口貼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定不會撕掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了就給我撕掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  也就是說你以真的樣子從千秋那裡得到創口貼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你以阿珍的樣子貼著同樣的創口貼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋就有可能會發現你的真實身份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之還是先把創口貼撕下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我已經決定了絕對不會把這個撕下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是千秋會發現你的真實身份的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  來玩黑白棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是玩的話  右手背會被看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼阿珍  要吃餅乾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個還是要用手的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創口貼要被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍一直對我擺著拒絕的姿勢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}拒\N絕\N的\N姿\N勢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前去海邊的時候明明關係還那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在已經討厭我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事  阿珍很珍惜千秋的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那個手勢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個姿勢一定是像萬歲什麼的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去認真確認友情吧  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  內田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把手藏起來的話不是這樣  而是要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手就還是…不要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  要我來代替千秋發言的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是阿珍你這蠢貨
